title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Shredder's Revenge Announced! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.10.21
description:
Blessing is joined by Janet Garcia for Mario Day 2021 to discuss Mario memories, a new TMNT brawler, Animal Crossing Build-a-bears, and more! 

Follow Janet: https://twitter.com/Gameonysus

00:00:00 - Start
00:12:49 - Housekeeping
There’s no FCF Draft tonight, but remember that the playoffs start THIS Saturday!
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Mick @DaNanoBiologist Abrahamson, Black Jack, & Trent Berrie
The Roper Report   -
00:13:33 - We’re getting a new Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles game! - Michael McWhertor @ Polygon
00:22:24 - Do you want to see more games done in this retro style but the game itself is brand new. Or keep seeing old remakes of games we already know like the Duck Tales game a few years ago? - Best Friends Q:Jordan Vickers
00:26:10 - Animal Crossing & Build-a-Bear are having a crossover - Rebekah Valentine @ IGN
00:31:35 - Don’t expect Elden Ring news in March - Francesco De Meo @ WCCFTech
00:37:15 - PS5 Developers Can Now Add Denuvo Anti-Cheat to Their Games - Jordan Oloman @ IGN
00:42:20 -  Ad
00:45:40 - We got more Outer Worlds DLC incoming
00:48:00 - Out today
00:59:45 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Tim and Tamoor Hussain
